a position to intervene.

00:05:13.855 --> 00:05:15.023 position:50% align:center
[MIYUKI]
I understand.

00:05:15.106 --> 00:05:17.942 position:50% align:center
I know you'll be at the
top of everybody's list!

00:05:18.026 --> 00:05:19.736 position:50% align:center
