both still in one piece?

00:06:59.961 --> 00:07:01.379 position:50% align:center
[SHIZUKU]
Apparently...

00:07:01.463 --> 00:07:02.922 position:50% align:center
[HONOKA]
Uh, um...

00:07:03.006 --> 00:07:05.050 position:50% align:center
