has my respect!

00:10:09.025 --> 00:10:12.570 position:50% align:center
[EIMI] Wow! There's an
army of them out there!

00:10:12.654 --> 00:10:14.406 position:50% align:center
I'm sure they're already
looking for you out there,

00:10:14.489 --> 00:10:15.907 position:50% align:center
